data.description: JUST LISTED! Discover tranquility in this charming Clayton residence. This home Features four spacious bedrooms, four full bathrooms, and a well-appointed kitchen with a gas range and elegant granite countertops. Entertain or relax on the screened-in back porch, perfect for outdoor living. Located in the sought-after Stone Briar community on a peaceful large cul-de-sac lot, this home offers a harmonious blend of community living and privacy. Plus, enjoy the convenience of nearby dining and shopping at Flowers Plantation. Don't miss the opportunity to call this your home.
